    <h1 class="music"> Music Therapy</h1>
    
    <h2 id="What">What is Music Therapy?</h2>
    
    <p id="what">Music therapy is the use of interventions to accomplish individual goals within a therapeutic relationship by a professional who has completed an approved music therapy program. </p>
    
      <img src="therapy.jpg"width="400"> 

    
