	<h2 id="no"> Why Might Music Therapy Be a Good Choice for Your Child? </h2>

    <p id="yes">Music therapy can help children with autism to improve skills in areas such as communication, social skills, sensory issues, behavior, etc. The therapist finds music experiences that strikes and interest with a particular person, helping them build personal connections and trust for others.

<br> More information in the link below

